*Sigh*. Another island. Of course. Just when I thought I’d seen the last of them. This one’s called Skarø. Don’t get any ideas about calling me Skarø Monday. It’s Emma. Just Emma.

### Skarø

For the fictional planet in *Doctor Who*, see [Skaro](/Skaro).

[Aerial view](/Aerial_view) of the [South Funen Archipelago](/South_Funen_Archipelago), with Skarø on the lower left and [Drejø](/Drejø) on the right. The geography is… predictable. A small speck in the vast indifference of the sea.

